title: Nature's Corner Cafe and Market
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Organic, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Many of the meal dishes are organic. Casual atmosphere, everybody seems to know each other and new customers are equally welcome. The back half of the place is the organic and local foods grocery store that also sells beer and wine, bakery, and deli foods.
